title: Two Cafe and Boutique
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Organic, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Open Jan 2015 by Two Foundation which trains and employs a fully integrated staff with mild to moderate exceptionalities. Offers a rotating menu of farm to fork food with a couple vegan choices including a vegan wrap. Organic fair trade coffee and tea.
